usage() {
  cat <<EOF
Usage: tools/mylite-mtr-harness [list|run|probe] [suite.test...]

Commands:
  list       Show curated MariaDB MTR smoke tests.
  run        Build the MTR smoke prerequisites and run exact selected tests.
             Defaults to the curated smoke list.
  probe      Build the MTR smoke prerequisites, run exact selected tests, and
             continue after failures. Exits nonzero if any test does not
             report an MTR pass. Removes newly generated .reject files.

Environment:
  BUILD_DIR          MariaDB build directory. Defaults to build/mariadb-mtr-smoke.
  PROFILE            Initial CMake cache. Defaults to cmake/mariadb-mtr-smoke.cmake.
  MTR_BUILD_THREAD  MTR build thread/port block. Defaults to auto.
  MTR_PROBE_TESTCASE_TIMEOUT_MINUTES
                     Probe testcase timeout passed to MTR. Defaults to 5.
EOF
}

